    "The survey results are presented in two formats: a bar chart and statistics.",
    "The results for all five aspects of the survey are in Additional File 1 as a bar chart, and statistical values are in Additional File 2.",
    "In all, 60 responses were obtained from institutions across the globe.",
    "The geographical distribution of the participants is indicated in Fig. 8.",
    "From the responses, it was noticed that 10 (16.7%) of the respondents had performed over 10 systematic reviews (SRs) over the past five years, 4 (6.7%) had conducted 7-10 reviews, while 22 (36.7%) had participated in 4-6 SRs and 24 (40%) had been involved in 1-3 SRs over the past years."
